item.title: StreamItV2
item.description: A web application that streams multimedia, both audio and video, which can be accessed by all registered users of the app. Users are able to modify media uploaded by them, but are not authorised to modify media uploaded by other users. Users with admin rights are able to freely add or delete media from the app. Users are also provided the functionality to upload and delete comments.
